# Code Owners for study-platform
# This file defines who should review pull requests for specific files/directories
# 
# When someone opens a pull request that modifies files with code owners,
# those owners are automatically requested as reviewers.
#
# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo
# This ensures that all PRs require review
